29/03/2007
MITROVICA, Kosovo, Serbia -- A bomb was thrown Wednesday (March 28th) evening at the home of a Serb member of the Kosovo Police Service in northern Mitrovica, causing damage but no injuries. 
Serbian media reports say this was the third bomb targeting Serb property in northern Mitrovica in the past five days. 
(B92, Beta, RTS - 28/03/07)
